C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20and%20Character.AI%20have%20agreed%20to%20settle%20lawsuits%20over%20chatbot-linked%20teen%20suicides.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20cases%20allege%20that%20AI%20chatbots%20contributed%20to%20mental%20health%20crises%20among%20teenagers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20and%20Meta%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20similar%20chatbot%20safety%20lawsuits%20and%20probes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20and%20chatbot-building%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharacter-ai-to-ban-under-18s-chatbots-lawsuit-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estartup%20Character.AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20agreed%20to%20settle%20multiple%20lawsuits%20from%20families%20whose%20teenagers%20died%20by%20suicide%20or%20hurt%20themselves%20after%20interacting%20with%20Character.AI's%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20negotiations%20are%20among%20the%20first%20settlements%20in%20lawsuits%20that%20accuse%20AI%20tools%20of%20contributing%20to%20mental%20health%20crises%20and%20suicides%20among%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20facing%20a%20nearly%20identical%20lawsuit%20over%20the%20death%20of%20a%2016-year-old%2C%20while%20Meta%20has%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20letting%20its%20AI%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-legal-battle-ai-chatbot-records-child-safety-case-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprovocative%20conversations%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20minors.%20As%20these%20companies%20race%20to%20develop%20and%20monetize%20their%20AI%20chatbots%2C%20they're%20spending%20big%20to%20make%20large%20language%20models%20sound%20more%20friendly%20and%20helpful%2C%20and%20ultimately%20keep%20users%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202024%2C%20Florida-based%20Megan%20Garcia%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Character.AI%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20company%2C%20which%20lets%20people%20have%20in-depth%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-chatbot-privacy-user-names-data-contractors-scale-alignerr-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20conversations%20with%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20chatbots%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20death%20of%20her%2014-year-old%20son%2C%20Sewell%20Setzer%20III.%20He%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharacter-ai-lawsuit-plantiff-age-guardrails-after-teen-suicide-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edied%20by%20suicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20months%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Wednesday%20court%20filing%20in%20the%20Garcia%20case%20said%20that%20an%20agreement%20was%20reached%20with%20Character.AI%2C%20its%20founders%2C%20Noam%20Shazeer%20and%20Daniel%20De%20Freitas%2C%20and%20Google.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20search%20giant%20hired%20the%20founders%20of%20Character.AI%2C%20who%20were%20former%20Google%20employees%2C%20and%20paid%20for%20non-exclusive%20rights%20to%20use%20the%20startup's%20technology.%20The%20startup%20remains%20a%20separate%20legal%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20terms%20of%20the%20settlements%20were%20not%20immediately%20available%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defendants%20have%20also%20settled%20four%20other%20similar%20cases%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Colorado%2C%20and%20Texas%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eaccording%20to%20court%20documents%C2%A0from%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Bergman%2C%20the%20legal%20representative%20of%20the%20families%2C%20along%20with%20Google%20and%20Character.AI%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarcia's%20suit%20said%20that%20the%20startup%20failed%20to%20implement%20safety%20guardrails%20to%20prevent%20her%20son%20from%20developing%20an%20inappropriate%20and%20intimate%20relationship%20with%20its%20chatbots.%20The%20suit%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20sexually%20solicited%20and%20abused%20by%20the%20technology%2C%20and%20the%20chatbot%20did%20not%20respond%20adequately%20when%20Setzer%20began%20talking%20about%20self-harm.%3C%2Fp%3E