5-day%20combat%20duty%2C%20each%20time%20at%20the%20request%20of%20a%20command%20and%20observation%20post%20in%20the%20local%20fighting%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRequests%20were%20received%20regularly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commander%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drone's%20primary%20objective%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeliver%20fire%20damage%20and%20fire%20suppression%20against%20the%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20discourage%20Russian%20troops%20from%20trying%20to%20advance%20in%20areas%20held%20by%20Ukraine%2C%20said%20Zinkevych.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Droid%20TW%2012.7%20would%20briefly%20leave%20its%20post%20every%20two%20days%20to%20be%20serviced%2C%20Zinkevych%20said%2C%20by%20a%20Ukrainian%20drone%20crew%20sheltering%20about%204%20kilometers%2C%20or%202.4%20miles%2C%20away%20from%20the%20line%20of%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20commander%2C%20technical%20maintenance%20took%20about%20four%20hours%20each%20time%2C%20including%20weapons%20servicing%2C%20restocking%20the%20drone's%20ammo%2C%20and%20recharging%20its%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20speed%20up%20the%20inspection%20process%2C%20over%20time%20we%20purchased%20additional%20battery%20packs%20at%20our%20own%20expense%2C%20which%20reduced%20the%20maintenance%20time%20to%202%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Zinkevych%20said.%20Ukrainian%20troops%20regularly%20spend%20their%20own%20salaries%20or%20savings%20on%20mat%C3%A9riel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevDroid%20says%20that%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-uncrewed-ground-vehicle-road-night-ambush-russian-m2-browning-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDroid%20TW%2012.7%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20an%20operational%20range%20of%20up%20to%2015%20miles%20and%20is%20controlled%20via%20a%20radio%20signal%2C%20but%20that%20the%20drone%20can%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20set%20its%20own%20course%20automatically.%20The%20extent%20to%20which%20it%20can%20autonomously%20navigate%20the%20battlefield%20and%20engage%20in%20combat%20is%20still%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Third%20Army%20Corps%20posted%20a%20video%20in%20December%20of%20the%20drone%20firing%20at%20an%20off-camera%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fjs%2Ftelegram-widget.js%3F22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20versions%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-approves-ground-robot-key-grenade-launchers-devdroid-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eground%20drone%20with%20grenade%20launchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Mk-19%20and%20AGL-53%2040mm%20%E2%80%94%20were%20also%20approved%20last%20month%20by%20Ukraine%20for%20official%20military%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZinkevych%20said%20that%20his%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unit-dedicated-fighting-russia-ground-assault-robots-ugvs-nc13-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreated%20in%20September%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20Third%20Assault%20Brigade%2C%20is%20focusing%20this%20year%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bmaximum%20involvement%26quot%3B%20and%20wider-scale%20use%20of%20UGVs%20in%20combat%20for%20both%20defensive%20and%20assault%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20for%20these%20systems%20is%20indeed%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Zinkevych%20said%20the%20process%20will%20be%20resource-intensive%2C%20and%20that%20his%20company%20runs%20a%20crowdfunding%20effort%20to%20continue%20developing%20its%20ground%20drones%20for%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20most%20cost-effective%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unit-ground-drone-devdroid-tw-fought-russians-45-days-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3